  m_Name: King - First Encounter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: King First Encounter
    lines:
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "...It\u2019s you. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'My liege. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'The kingdom is gone. Why have you returned? There is nothing left for
        you to destroy. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I\u2019m here for you. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "You\u2019ve already slain me. Perhaps for you, the memory became buried
        under all of the other lives you\u2019ve taken, but Isovios\u2019 blade still
        burns in my chest. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I\u2019m here for your aid. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: '...Explain yourself. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "It\u2019s been a long time since I last saw you. I\u2019ve seen things
        since we couldn\u2019t have even conceived of as boys \u2013 kingdoms as
        high as mountains, inventions beyond comprehension, territories swapping
        hands time and time again, until the maps we grew up with became foreign. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'The sword. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "That\u2019s right. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "Then I ask again: why do you return here? You desecrated my family\u2019s
        heirloom and lived to see the wonders of the future. What more could you
        want? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'I have lived and relived millennia of my misdeeds, witnessed innumerable
        souls suffer by my hand. It is time to put an end to it. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'An end... how? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I am not strong enough alone to stop the evils I unleashed on this land.
        I have made amends with others like you, and, through coalescence, we\u2019ve
        already undone many of my past faults. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'With your shield and your light, we can make right what remains of my
        mistakes. We can take down Scathe, mend things here in Caladria. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "And I\u2019m to believe this isn\u2019t a trick? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'I have nothing left to gain. I have outlived the entire world, and there
        is nothing left for me at the end of it but a barren wasteland. Traveling
        back to our time is a gift I intend not to waste. Please, join me in my fight. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "We were to fight cheek by jowl. I chose you, Orion, to be my advisor,
        my right hand, my knight. Look around you. This is the aftermath of my trust
        in you\u2026 Leave me to wander my broken kingdom. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "Caspian, I beg of you: I have righted many of my wrongs, but this haunts
        me most of all. Allow me this chance to fix what I\u2019ve done to you. Please. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "Can\u2019t you find someone else? Why must it be me? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "It\u2019s as you said: we were meant to fight side by side. I failed
        you before, but I will finally fulfill my duty of protecting you by putting
        a stop to all of it. This, I promise. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: '... '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: '...I will lend you my hand. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
